# {{APP_NAME}}

## Build

Interactive menu:

```
build\Menu.bat
```

Or directly:

```powershell
powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File build\Build.ps1
```

Output: `build/{{APP_NAME}}/{{APP_NAME}}.exe`

## Installer

Inno Setup 6 must be installed at `C:\Program Files (x86)\Inno Setup 6\`.

```powershell
powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File build\Installer.ps1
```

Output: `build/Installer/{{APP_NAME}}-Setup-<version>.exe` (version comes from `<Version>` in `Directory.Build.props`)

